<br>
We also believe that Christ &quot;saved&quot; us from the fall with his atonement.  We believe everyone will be resurrected whether they accept Jesus or not, He gave that to everyone as a gift.<br>
<br>
We believe that we existed as spirits with God before being born here and that we all chose to follow him and chose to come to come here to mortality in order to progress.  Therefore, spiritually, whether they are able to follow through on this or not once they are in mortality and subject to temptation, we all get here inherently good from the start, it's just a matter of whether we improve further upon ourselves and help and love each other along while we are here.  Remember that LDS have  a broader view of salvation and we believe everything we make of ourselves here stays a part of who we are after we die.<br>
